{"tid":399463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"細妹話想申請學生信用卡","createTime":"2017-09-14T03:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T05:28:21.000Z","uid":127586,"like":9,"dislike":258,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21096300f125620038cfb93434b36853c19811b2","tid":399463,"uid":127586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:33:22.000Z","msg":"細妹話想申請信用卡 <br />\n我自己就無信用卡 因為始終怕有卡數負債<br />\n但係細妹堅持想要 又話買野方便 仲可以捐錢乜乜柒柒 <br />\n佢仲要係岩岩上asshole 18歲 兼職揾得雞碎咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我唔想佢到時又俾麻煩屋企 <br />\n我究竟應唔應該比佢申請好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9522e388283217bdd5086f72190d92f5295578eb","tid":399463,"uid":127586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4976f0b05afaff0011ebf7486a4288af0b4356","tid":399463,"uid":127586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f606db549636687300e9764358fd64cd3564c0ec","tid":399463,"uid":107571,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"佢都夠年齡負擔<br />\n比佢申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f014f30602178a85d66c753f9cab6e2052f14946","tid":399463,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"佢自己申請左你都唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64be86bd21121631ce83d8d85af72763fe4f6356","tid":399463,"uid":127586,"like":9,"dislike":16,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢都夠年齡負擔<br />\n比佢申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n年齡夠唔代表心智夠 就係擔心佢去申請完之後勁大使"},{"pid":"7063ffbdcd90f637192f1d2de800918f463aa07c","tid":399463,"uid":45773,"like":230,"dislike