br />\n要大洗唔申請張信用卡都大洗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1dd93f3cc229819f3839c063e6a0512ac0f148","tid":399463,"uid":55941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真 有張卡放便好多<br />\n淨係買戲飛都唔洗煩"},{"pid":"c5e6fd856d106c64c822f473151e3ffcdc35fc3a","tid":399463,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地夠18歲申唔申請關你撚事？洗撚你批準？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還唔到咪做雞囉<br />\n睇個樣都係雞格架喇"},{"pid":"ea3989d8d4d13b901b3f72113dd55fbf0508c399","tid":399463,"uid":67329,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"你都係驚日後有咩依郁你要幫手找數啫<br />\n<br />\n盡早同佢割蓆話到時唔撚同你找數咪得<br />\n<br />\n講真 學生卡credit得果一皮有幾多手尾"},{"pid":"d89cb6e5c696ab82946dc4e7695eb877a4f05b21","tid":399463,"uid":65408,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"你唔識理財唔代表你個妹都唔識"},{"pid":"5883d35458958c5daf8b6871d184bf626a84876f","tid":399463,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野年代 申請張信用卡都驚呢樣個樣<br />\n廢老思想 出夜街=學壞 去唱k=做雞<br />\n要大洗唔申請張信用卡都大洗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能已經做緊"},{"pid":"a09c329949a588f2667e1ae375aa60365c327f8c","tid":399463,"uid":45773,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地夠18歲申唔申請關你撚事？洗撚你批準？</blockquote><br />\n我係佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時出咗事邊個負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個妹話要你負責？</blockquote><br />\n佢咁細過可以點負責 其他屋企人都表示唔理佢</blockquote><br />\n姐係你自以為個妹一定會出事，然後假設佢一定還唔到，之後就想單方面剝削個妹申請信用卡嘅權利，最後就自以為幫緊個妹，你條契弟仲父權過你老豆，比個叻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4837042ab052284657a2509eb68856345e83dc","tid":399463,"uid":128563,"like":5,"dislike":77,"score":-72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"好老實講，一個正常學生其實係完全冇必要用信用卡。<br />\n<br />\n首先係信用卡本身係俾大筆數先話方便，學生最大筆嘅支出應該都係買iPhone幾千銀。其他時候幾百蚊同攞現金俾錢一樣冇話邊樣方便啲。<br />\n<br />\n其次，學生有幾多就洗幾多，冇需要用信用卡找數。冇咁多錢就唔好洗，信用卡係俾找到卡數嘅人用，俾慣咗min pay係一定返唔到轉頭。"},{"pid":"ca3f38a9d8e9f5215f4b85c8b3ce74427019c82e","tid":399463,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地夠18歲申唔申請關你撚事？洗撚你批準？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還唔到咪做雞囉<br />\n睇個樣都係雞格架喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a063d44da42e62853a255f2af933306f10b0ca","tid":399463,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地夠18歲申唔申請關你撚事？洗撚你批準？</blockquote><br />\n我係佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時出咗事邊個負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個妹話要你負責？</blockquote><br />\n佢咁細過可以點負責 其他屋企人都表示唔理佢</blockquote><br />\n成年人 自己應該要識諗 對自己行為負責<br />\n你都應該唔好再咁保護佢 俾返d責任佢自己負責返<br />\n呢個已經唔係信唔信用卡既問題"},{"pid":"b035b9325634b1549e2ae7360629208353fca19b","tid":399463,"uid":26385,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老實講，一個正常學生其實係完全冇必要用信用卡。<br />\n<br />\n首先係信用卡本身係俾大筆數先話方便，學生最大筆嘅支出應該都係買iPhone幾千銀。其他時候幾百蚊同攞現金俾錢一樣冇話邊樣方便啲。<br />\n<br />\n其次，學生有幾多就洗幾多，冇需要用信用卡找數。冇咁多錢就唔好洗，信用卡係俾找到卡數嘅人用，俾慣咗min pay係一定返唔到轉頭。</blockquote><br />\n你咪用現金買機票同訂酒店囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經唔講好多時用卡有優惠<br />\n只係買野方便呢點已經無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上hktv買野都要信用卡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲老野思想真係害人不淺<br />\n開卡=還min pay<br />\n咁食飯係咪即係食屎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbebc0be043bea9c9bce0e313d3902b4bfc1a55","tid":399463,"uid":134462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:49:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ff41f7aa5581b161248490fb1d50786af5d70a0","tid":399463,"uid":20903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"廢老思維<br />\n大唔大洗根本唔關張咭事"},{"pid":"b9bb64ab067673dabe3cf47eadbdf228a1246732","tid":399463,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:50:11.000Z","msg":"又一隻準ptg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e402fab8e13f705d39ecba12b7fdaf62874cd0","tid":399463,"uid":13809,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"點解2017年仲有咁多人對信用卡有恐懼<br />\n會唔會俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e43cbd88b9ccfaa41f4e85675ed45ea0bee0a8","tid":399463,"uid":26385,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老思維<br />\n大唔大洗根本唔關張咭事</blockquote><br />\n其實都幾震驚<br />\n廿幾歲𡃁仔諗野都成個廢老咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你自己唔用唔緊要<br />\n連人地用都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94246333ef6b1383669e79dcf1f766fbaff8823","tid":399463,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢都夠年齡負擔<br />\n比佢申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n年齡夠唔代表心智夠 就係擔心佢去申請完之後勁大使</blockquote><br />\n勁大使咪自己還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"